<h3>Peracence: A Medieval Marvel</h3>
<p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-27270" src="https://spainguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Peracence-Aaragon.jpg" alt="Peracence - Aragon" width="830" height="530" srcset="https://spainguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Peracence-Aaragon.jpg 830w, https://spainguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Peracence-Aaragon-300x192.jpg 300w, https://spainguides.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Peracence-Aaragon-768x490.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 830px) 100vw, 830px" /></p>
