	<h4>Pro-Tip</h4>
<hr />
<p>For a special family day out with some freshly made tortilla and a drink or two, head to the <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Fonts+de+l'Algar/@38.6604987,-0.0952624,19z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0xd61f89875c768d5:0x8bc5c3fbd5537413!8m2!3d38.6604652!4d-0.0948788!16s%2Fg%2F11_tt0jk1?entry=ttu" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Algar Waterfalls</a>, a serene oasis not far from Benidorm. Discover the beauty of a tumbling waterfall, surrounded by picnic spots, and a river perfect for splashing and swimming in the mid-day heat.</p>
